verbose_text: Thus, high-dimensional CyTOF analysis revealed that despite the similar overall abundance of myeloid cells in CTRL and tumor bearing MGs, the ILC like tumors in Cdh f/f; R26-Pik3ca Mut +/-; Wap-Cre mice promoted macrophages to adopt a unique differentiation state in the MG.
evidence: Wap-Cre mice promoted macrophages to adopt a unique differentiation
